parameters:
I heard there's a girl who stayed alone at the timber
lodging in Suranashi Village and ended up pregnant. Maybe
she was attacked while she was asleep. Scary, huh.

Miss, this is no time to be stopping by such a poor lodging
house. Hurry and evacuate from Edo. There's no need to throw
away your young life.

This is a lodging house for workers. If you're not okay with
sleeping in a communal space, you won't be able to stay
here.

Oh no! Is the world coming to an end already? I wanted to
experience a wonderful romance... *sniffle*...

They say there's a fisherman who saw a ridiculously huge
octopus called the "Ghost Octopus" off the coast of Uraga.
Is that true?

Even if I wanted to escape by boat, my ship's been stolen...
I can't go on unless I drown my sorrows in booze... *hic*.

I work at the docks every day to save up money. That's why
this cheap lodging house is such a lifesaver. But it's tough
to sleep when someone next to you is snoring loudly...

It's no use running away now. I love this Edo, so I'll stay
here until the very end.

(...Such loud snoring. There's no way I can sleep next to
someone like this.)

...Seriously, what a ridiculous situation. It's so scary I
might just go back to sleep... Yeah, a second round of
defiant slumber, that's what it is.
